trans-unit.source: Provides an interface for developers to specify custom editing controls that are associated with a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Gir et grensesnitt for utviklere å angi egendefinerte redigering kontroller som er knyttet til en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The IWebEditable interface enables you to associate custom <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> controls with a server control--such as a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control, a user control, or a custom server control.
trans-unit.target: Grensesnittet IWebEditable gjør det mulig å knytte egendefinerte <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>Kontroller med serverkontroll, for eksempel en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontroll, en kontroll eller en egendefinert serverkontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> controls are contained with an <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZone> control, and this zone with its editing controls provides end users with a user interface (UI) for modifying properties, appearance, and behavior on the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>Kontroller finnes med en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZone>kontrollerer, og denne sonen med redigering kontrollene gir sluttbrukere brukergrensesnittet (UI) for å endre egenskaper, utseendet og virkemåten for den tilknyttede <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZone> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>

trans-unit.source: The IWebEditable interface includes two exposed members.
trans-unit.target: Grensesnittet IWebEditable inneholder to eksponerte medlemmer.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebEditable.WebBrowsableObject%2A> property provides a way for <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> controls to get a reference to the associated server control.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebEditable.WebBrowsableObject%2A>egenskapen inneholder en metode for <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>Kontroller for å hente en referanse til den tilknyttede serverkontrollen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebEditable.WebBrowsableObject%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebEditable.CreateEditorParts%2A> method is used to create an instance of each custom <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> control associated with a server control, and return them as a collection.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebEditable.CreateEditorParts%2A>metoden brukes til å opprette en forekomst av hver egendefinerte <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>kontrollen som er tilknyttet en serverkontroll og Tilbakestill dem som en samling.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebEditable.CreateEditorParts%2A>

trans-unit.source: The IWebEditable interface is already implemented on the base <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> class, although by default this implementation does not associate any custom <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> controls with the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> class.
trans-unit.target: Grensesnittet IWebEditable er allerede implementert på den grunnleggende <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>class, selv om denne implementeringen som standard ikke knytte eventuelle egendefinerte <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>Kontroller med <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>klasse.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: To associate a derived <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control with custom <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> controls, you can override the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebEditable.CreateEditorParts%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Å knytte en avledet <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontroll med egendefinerte <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>kontroller, du kan overstyre den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebEditable.CreateEditorParts%2A>metoden.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebEditable.CreateEditorParts%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: Returns a collection of custom <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart"></xref> controls associated with a server control that implements the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebEditable"></xref> interface.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer en samling av egendefinerte <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart"> </xref> Kontroller knyttet til en serverkontroll som implementerer den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebEditable"> </xref> grensesnitt.

trans-unit.source: The CreateEditorParts method enables you to create a collection of all the custom <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> controls associated with your custom control, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control, or user control, and return them as an <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartCollection> object.
trans-unit.target: Metoden CreateEditorParts kan du opprette en samling av egendefinert <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>Kontroller knyttet til den egendefinerte kontrollen <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontroll eller bruker kontrollere og Tilbakestill dem som en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartCollection>objektet.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control takes the collection and creates instances of all the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> controls whenever the server control enters edit mode.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>kontrollen tar samlingen og oppretter forekomster av alle de <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>Kontroller når serverkontrollen går inn i redigeringsmodus.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: Typically you implement this method in a custom <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control by overriding its <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.CreateEditorParts%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Vanligvis Implementer denne metoden i en egendefinert <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontroll av overstyrer den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.CreateEditorParts%2A>metoden.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.CreateEditorParts%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: In the method, you create instances of the custom <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> controls you want to associate with your controls, add them to an <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartCollection> object, and then return that object.
trans-unit.target: I metoden, oppretter du forekomster av egendefinert <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>Kontroller du vil knytte til din Kontroller legge dem til en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartCollection>objekt, og deretter går tilbake dette objektet.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>

trans-unit.source: The collection of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> controls is then assigned to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneBase.EditorParts%2A> property of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneBase> zone.
trans-unit.target: Samlingen av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>Kontroller tilordnes deretter den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneBase.EditorParts%2A>for den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneBase>sone.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneBase> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneBase.EditorParts%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Any <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> that is added to the collection of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> controls in an implementation of the CreateEditorParts method must have a value assigned to its ID property, otherwise an exception will be thrown when the collection is assigned to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneBase.EditorParts%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Noen <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>som er lagt til i samlingen av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>Kontroller i en implementering av metoden CreateEditorParts må ha en verdi som er tilordnet til egenskapen ID, ellers vil bli utløst et unntak under samlingen er tilordnet til den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneBase.EditorParts%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneBase.EditorParts%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartCollection"></xref> that contains the collection of custom <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart"></xref> controls associated with a server control.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartCollection"> </xref> som inneholder samlingen av egendefinerte <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart"> </xref> Kontroller knyttet til en serverkontroll.

trans-unit.source: Gets a reference to the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> control, user control, or custom control that will be edited by <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart"></xref> controls.
trans-unit.target: Henter en referanse til det <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> kontroll, brukerkontrollen eller egendefinert kontroll som redigeres av <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart"> </xref> kontroller.

trans-unit.source: The WebBrowsableObject property provides a way for <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> controls to get a reference to the server controls they are associated with.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen WebBrowsableObject inneholder en metode for <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>Kontroller for å hente en referanse til serverkontroller tilknyttede.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>

trans-unit.source: Although the property itself is read-only, the object reference that it returns enables <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> controls to change values in the server control.
trans-unit.target: Selv om selve egenskapen er skrivebeskyttet, objektreferansen den returnerer aktiverer <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>Kontroller for å endre verdiene i serverkontrollen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>

trans-unit.source: An object reference to the control associated with an <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: En objektreferanse til kontrollen som er tilknyttet en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart"> </xref> kontrollen.
